Game controls:
Move player left and right - Joystick shift
Select button - Green button
Pause button - Red button
Navigate through buttons - Joystick shift


Elixirs:
Elixirs spawn on "Normal" difficulty:
Red elixir spawns every 10th time 2nd tile is initialized and it gives player a shield from 1 cannon shot.
Green elixir spawns every 10th time 3rd tile is initialized and it gives player 2x coin multiplier for 30 seconds.

Cannons:
Cannons start shooting when player steps on that tile and they shoot in intervals between 1-3 seconds.
Be aware that some cannons are hidden!

End:
The game is made as endless runner so it has no end.
You run until you don't, GOOD LUCK!
